1563
02:14:43.466 --> 02:14:44.789
Yes. friend?

1564
02:14:46.270 --> 02:14:49.933
not sure what to say.
so I'm just going to...

1565
02:14:58.081 --> 02:14:59.042
Grace?

1566
02:15:03.166 --> 02:15:04.488
No one to watch you sleep.

1567
02:15:06.148 --> 02:15:06.709
Yeah.

1568
02:15:09.112 --> 02:15:11.533
You are very brave.

1569
02:15:14.037 --> 02:15:15.959
I don't know about that.

1570
02:15:18.962 --> 02:15:22.505
You are the bravest
human I have ever met.

1571
02:15:24.186 --> 02:15:25.148
Hey.

1572
02:15:25.648 --> 02:15:26.349
It's a joke.

1573
02:15:26.349 --> 02:15:27.170
I know.

1574
02:15:27.970 --> 02:15:30.733
I only meet one
human. and it's you.

1575
02:15:30.813 --> 02:15:31.714
I get it.

1576
02:15:32.495 --> 02:15:33.175
It's a good joke.

1577
02:15:33.695 --> 02:15:34.276
Good joke.

1578
02:15:35.737 --> 02:15:36.318
All right.

1579
02:15:42.163 --> 02:15:43.405
Well... Goodbye.

1580
02:15:45.107 --> 02:15:46.488
No understand word.

1581
02:15:48.130 --> 02:15:49.812
See you later.

1582
02:15:50.232 --> 02:15:51.473
But I won't see you later.

1583
02:15:56.317 --> 02:15:57.158
I know.

1584
02:16:00.262 --> 02:16:01.983
How do you say
goodbye back home?

1585
02:16:03.104 --> 02:16:03.484
We don't.

1586
02:16:05.406 --> 02:16:07.008
We do this.

1587
02:17:58.837 --> 02:18:05.022
Journey to Earth will take four
years. two months. and eleven days.

1588
02:18:44.548 --> 02:18:52.930
Contamined. detected.

1589
02:18:46.233 --> 02:18:48.156
<i>{\an8}Grace</i>

1590
02:18:59.675 --> 02:19:18.194
Contaminant detected.

1591
02:19:21.225 --> 02:19:23.116
<i>{\an8}‫Engines Shutting Down</i>

1592
02:19:28.371 --> 02:19:30.021
<i>{\an8}Depressurization in progress
WARNING</i>

1593
02:20:02.356 --> 02:20:03.356
There's a leak.

1594
02:20:05.979 --> 02:20:06.820
The problem is the xenonite.

1595
02:20:08.262 --> 02:20:09.882
The Taumoeba can get through it.

1596
02:20:10.944 --> 02:20:13.366
Probably because we bred it
in the xenonite breeder tanks

1597
02:20:13.587 --> 02:20:14.868
it evolved to escape it.

1598
02:20:15.889 --> 02:20:18.812
I was able to stop it before it
ate all the astrophage on the ship.

1599
02:20:21.755 --> 02:20:23.296
Rocky's ship is
built of xenonite.

1600
02:20:24.638 --> 02:20:27.160
The Taumoeba will already
be in its fuel lines.

1601
02:20:28.461 --> 02:20:31.164
He won't be able to find the leak
because the leak is the ship itself.

1602
02:20:31.904 --> 02:20:35.248
He'll be without
any fuel. Stranded.

1603
02:20:35.828 --> 02:20:37.729
His life support
systems will fail.

1604
02:20:40.432 --> 02:20:43.194
If that doesn't kill him
the radiation sickness will.

1605
02:20:46.499 --> 02:20:49.882
He's looking at a long. slow.

1606
02:20:51.724 --> 02:20:53.606
painful death.

1607
02:20:56.568 --> 02:20:56.769
Alone.

1608
02:21:07.424 --> 02:21:09.106
<i>{\an8}Who am I?</i>

1609
02:21:13.675 --> 02:21:15.168
<i>Intercept time</i>

1610
02:21:17.474 --> 02:21:18.897
<i>56.187 days</i>

1611
02:21:20.852 --> 02:21:22.173
I can't do both.

1612
02:21:24.335 --> 02:21:25.276
I can go home.

1613
02:21:28.999 --> 02:21:30.321
Or I can save

1614
02:21:49.940 --> 02:21:52.863
I've sent you detailed
logs of all of our findings

1615
02:21:53.564 --> 02:21:56.446
and enough Taumoeba
for you to start

1616
02:21:56.446 --> 02:21:58.008
your very own Taumoeba farm.

1617
02:21:57.890 --> 02:21:59.798
<i>{\an8}‫Ringo</i>

1618
02:22:01.511 --> 02:22:02.752
At least I never
have to hear you say.

1619
02:22:03.012 --> 02:22:04.254
I told you so.

1620
02:22:05.795 --> 02:22:07.216
Even though you were right.

1621
02:22:09.381 --> 02:22:10.195
<i>{\an8}George</i>

1622
02:22:10.220 --> 02:22:11.141
<i>{\an8}‫John</i>

1623
02:22:11.166 --> 02:22:12.119
<i>{\an8}Paul</i>

1624
02:22:12.144 --> 02:22:13.355
<i>{\an8}Ringo</i>

1625
02:25:48.571 --> 02:25:50.894
I'm here. buddy.

1626
02:26:13.596 --> 02:26:18.100
Earth. Rocky. Rocky. Earth.

1627
02:26:18.100 --> 02:26:20.602
Hello. Earth. I am Rocky.

1628
02:26:20.602 --> 02:26:25.206
I am Rocky from Erid. I am not
Rocky from movie. No. no. no. no.

1629
02:26:25.206 --> 02:26:28.530
I'm pretty sure they know that.

1630
02:26:28.610 --> 02:26:32.813
I left you detailed logs of all of our findings.
and I threw in a little something else just for fun.

1631
02:26:35.577 --> 02:26:37.037
Hopefully it all makes sense.

1632
02:26:38.319 --> 02:26:40.361
And if not. you're smart.

1633
02:26:42.062 --> 02:26:43.004
You'll figure it out.

1634
02:26:44.766 --> 02:26:48.489
This is Dr. Captain Ryland
Grace reporting from the Hail Mary.

1635
02:26:48.629 --> 02:26:50.631
As the Eridians say...

1636
02:27:07.647 --> 02:27:08.628
Let's begin.

1637
02:27:24.483 --> 02:27:26.649
<i>‫Peanut Butter</i>

1638
02:27:26.679 --> 02:27:28.259
<i>‫Taumoeba Farm</i>

1639
02:28:01.279 --> 02:28:02.620
Good morning. Armando.

1640
02:28:04.102 --> 02:28:05.143
You shouldn't have.

1641
02:28:11.669 --> 02:28:15.674
That's a noogie. I'm coming!

1642
02:28:20.883 --> 02:28:22.971
Why you take so long?

1643
02:28:23.280 --> 02:28:24.342
Why you always
gotta be so early?

1644
02:28:24.051 --> 02:28:26.053
I knock and I knock.

1645
02:28:25.843 --> 02:28:28.705
Yeah. I know. and I ignored you.

1646
02:28:28.848 --> 02:28:29.724
Grace. the door.

1647
02:28:29.748 --> 02:28:31.750
Close the door.

1648
02:28:32.810 --> 02:28:35.372
Why? I thought this
was a safe neighborhood.

1649
02:28:35.312 --> 02:28:36.898
I make door. You close door.

1650
02:28:36.894 --> 02:28:39.617
Okay. Armando
likes the fresh air.

1651
02:28:53.350 --> 02:28:55.753
Can we talk about the water
temperature a little bit?

1652
02:28:55.666 --> 02:28:56.750
Yes.

1653
02:28:56.674 --> 02:28:59.696
It's amazing just that
you've done it at all.

1654
02:29:01.117 --> 02:29:01.838
Very cold.

1655
02:29:02.758 --> 02:29:04.520
And before it was boiling.

1656
02:29:05.401 --> 02:29:06.282
Is there an in-between?

1657
02:29:07.302 --> 02:29:08.636
I ask Adrian to work on this.

1658
02:29:15.111 --> 02:29:19.895
Please tell the bio-dome
illumination team that it's perfect now.

1659
02:29:20.565 --> 02:29:23.068
You no want it sunnier than this?

1660
02:29:22.498 --> 02:29:26.261
Oh no. this is. you know
I'm a sucker for the fog.

1661
02:29:35.955 --> 02:29:37.038
Grace.

1662
02:29:36.871 --> 02:29:38.273
Yapa.

1663
02:29:39.291 --> 02:29:42.043
Eridian scientists are ready...

1664
02:29:42.085 --> 02:29:44.339
to prepare Hail Mary for journey home.

1665
02:29:52.388 --> 02:29:53.608
Can I think about it?

1666
02:29:55.307 --> 02:29:57.642
Yes. think about it long time.

1667
02:30:43.797 --> 02:30:46.640
Good morning. class.

1668
02:30:47.621 --> 02:30:51.284
Okay. Everyone.
take their seats.

1669
02:30:52.325 --> 02:30:53.607
Let's wake up.

1670
02:30:57.510 --> 02:30:59.052
Who can tell me
the speed of light?
